    "description": "Continuous CyberBattleSim (C-CyberBattleSim) is an advanced extension of Microsoft’s CyberBattleSim, introducing an embedding model that supports continuous state and action spaces. This enhancement enables the development of more scalable and generalizable reinforcement learning agents for cyber attack path prediction. The framework also includes an expanded scenario generation pipeline and a unified system for training and evaluation. ",
